label: Carson Valley Times
title: Carson_Valley_Times
exrest: The Carson Valley Times (CVT) was an American daily online newspaper and group of journalistic publications, published in Gardnerville, Nevada from July 2013 through September 2017. It was one of three newspapers published in the Carson Valley along with the Record-Courier and the Sierra Scoop. It was a member of the Nevada Press Association.
